ats that's fine Lunatic, post it in a separate thread next time since my post was about end game and being satisfied with the visual appearence of your character besides the fact that different races of the same class get the same amount of hp per point of sta.<br><br>Kamlatir,<br>Grave Lord of Far Seekers, The Rathe<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Tue Apr 30 19:09:38 2002</em></p>&nbsp;<br></td></td></tr>
